Suncani Hvar Jumps for Fifth Day, Extending March Rally to 134%

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-03-22T10:14:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/suncani-hvar-jumps-for-fifth-day-extending-march-rally-to-134-.html
Suncani Hvar d.d. (SUNHRA) , a Croatian hotel
operator, rose to the highest in more than two years and headed
for its biggest monthly rally on record.  The stock jumped for a fifth day, adding 19 percent to 69
kuna as of 11:10 a.m. in Zagreb, its highest intraday price
since November 2008. Suncani Hvar has gained 91 percent in the
past five days, extending its advance in March to 134 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  